\v 6 So Yahweh¦312721 declares that the time¦312717 is coming¦312718 when this place¦312725 will no longer be called¦312724 Tofet¦312728 or the Valley of Ben-Hinnom, but¦312722 \add rather\add*, the ‘Valley of Slaughter’.
\v 7 Then¦312739 I'll confound Yehudah¦312743 and Yerushalem's¦312744 plans in this place¦312745, and I'll \add ≈have them struck down by their enemies' swords¦312748\add* and by those¦312752 who \add ≈want to kill them\add*, and I'll give¦312754 their dead bodies to the birds and the wild animals¦312761 for food.
\v 8 Then¦312764 I'll¦312764 make¦312764 that city¦312767 into a wasteland¦312769 \add ≈that's something to scoff at\add*—everyone¦312771 who passes¦312772 by will be appalled¦312774 and¦312764 will \add ≈mock it because of all its¦312780 disasters\add*.
