\v 4 because if you carefully¦313685 do those things¦313689, then the kings¦313695 who sit on David's¦313697 throne¦313700 will enter through the gates¦313692 of this palace riding in chariots¦313702 or on horses¦313703, \add ≈along with\add* their officials and their people¦313707.
