\v 3 Then¦314252 I myself will gather¦314253 the remnant¦314256 of my flock¦314257 from all the \add ≈countries\add* that I've¦314262 banished¦314262 them to and I'll¦314253 return them to their¦314269 pasture¦314269, where¦314260 they'll be fruitful¦314270 and multiply.
\v 4 Yahweh¦314288 declares that I'll¦314273 \add ≈appoint\add* shepherds¦314275 over them who'll \add ≈look after\add* them, and¦314273 then¦314273 they'll no longer be afraid¦314279 or dismayed, nor will any go missing¦314285.
