\p
\v 7 Listen, Yahweh declares that the \add ≈time¦314329 is\add* coming¦314330 when they'll no longer say¦314336, ‘As surely as Yahweh lives, who brought¦314342 the \add ≈Israelis¦314345\add* out from Egypt¦314348.’
\v 8 \add ≈Instead\add* \add ≡they'll say\add*, ‘As surely as Yahweh¦314355 lives, who brought and led the \add ≈Israelis¦314363\add* out of the land in the north¦314366 and all the other lands¦314368 that¦314358 he'd banished¦314370 them to.’ Then they'll live in their¦314375 own land again.
