\v 13 Among the prophets in Shomrom¦314459 \add (Samaria¦314459)\add*, I've seen \add ≈offensive¦314461 behaviour\add*:
\q1 they prophesied¦314462 by Baal¦314463 and¦314458 led my people¦314467 Yisrael¦314470 astray.
