\q1 They commit¦314477 adultery¦314477 and walk in lies.
\q1 They \add ≈empower those who do evil¦314487\add*,
\q1 →so that no one turns their¦314491 back on wickedness.
\q1 They're all like Sodom¦314492 to me.
\q1 ≈The people in Jerusalem are like Gomorrah¦314494,
\q1
\v 15 therefore this is what Commander-in-chief Yahweh¦314501 says¦314500 about¦314507 the prophets:
\q1 I'll¦314510 feed them wormwood¦314509
\q1 ≈and give them poisoned¦314513 water¦314511 to drink¦314510,
\q1 because¦314514 ungodliness has spread throughout the land
