\v 16 This is what Commander-in-chief Yahweh¦314528 says¦314527:
\q1 Don't¦314530 listen¦314532 to the words¦314535 of the prophets who prophesy to you.
\q1 They are filling you all with false hopes.
\q1 They speak¦314544 visions¦314542 from their own minds,
\q1 not from Yahweh's¦314528 mouth¦314546.
