\v 19 Then¦318464 thanksgiving¦318466 will go¦318464 out from them,
\q1 ≈and the sound¦318467 of those laughing.
\q1 I'll multiply¦318469 them, and they won't diminish¦318471 \add in number\add*,
\q1 →and I'll make¦318472 them honoured¦318472—
\q1 ≈they won't become insignificant¦318474.
\q1
\v 20 Then¦318476 its children¦318477 will be as in \add ≈former times\add*,
\q1 and its community will be established¦318481 \add ≈under my supervision\add*,
\q1 and I'll¦318482 punish \add ≈all those¦318486 who oppress¦318486 it\add*.
\q1
\v 21 Its \add ≈king\add* will be from among it,
\q1 ≈and its ruler¦318491 will come¦318493 from its middle.
\q1 Then¦318488 I'll¦318494 bring¦318494 it near, and it will approach me,
