\v 22 You'll¦318515 be my people¦318514
\q1 and¦318515 I'll¦318516 become¦318516 your god¦318518.
\p
\v 23 Listen¦318521, Yahweh's¦318524 storm of rage¦318525 has gone out—
\q1 a storm whirling¦318532 around the \add #heads\add* of wicked¦318531 \add people\add*.
