\c 31
\s1 Yisrael's return home
\rem /s1 Hope for Restoration; Israel's Return Home; The Joyful Return of the Exiles
\p
\v 1 Yahweh¦318557 declares that at that time¦318553, I'll¦318558 be \add the\add* god¦318559 to all of Yisrael's¦318562 \add ≈families\add*, and¦318563 they'll be my people¦318567.
\v 2 Yahweh¦318572 says¦318571 this:
\q1 A people¦318576, the survivors¦318577 \add ≈after being attacked in war\add*,
\q1 found¦318573 favour¦318574 in the wilderness¦318575,
