\q1
\v 3 From far off, Yahweh¦318584 appeared¦318585 to me: I've always¦318588 loved¦318589 you
\q1 therefore¦318590 I've \add ≈displayed\add* loyal¦318594 commitment \add ≈to help you endure\add*.
\q1
\v 4 I'll¦318597 rebuild¦318598 you, and you'll be \add ≈restored\add*, Yisrael's \add ≈pretty daughter\add*.
\q1 Again¦318596 you'll adorn¦318602 yourself¦318602 with your tambourines¦318603,
