\v 6 \add ≈Yes,\add* there'll¦318618 be a day¦318620 when the watchers¦318622 in the Efrayim hill country¦318623 will call¦318621 out,
\q1 ‘\add ≈Get ready\add* and¦318626 let's go¦318626 up to our¦318631 god¦318631 Yahweh¦318630 at Tsiyyon¦318627 \add (Zion¦318627)\add*,’
