\v 7 because¦318634 Yahweh says¦318638 this:
\q1 “Sing for \add Yisrael\add* (Yakov) with gladness¦318642,
\q1 ≈and shout for this \add ≈leader\add* of the nations¦318645.
\q1 Cause it to be heard, praise¦318647, and say¦318648,
\q1 ‘Yahweh, save¦318649 your¦318653 people¦318653, the remnant¦318655 of Yisrael.’
\q1
\v 8 Listen, I'm bringing¦318659 them \add back\add* from the land¦318661 in the north¦318662,
\q1 ≈and I'll¦318663 gather¦318663 them from the remote¦318664 parts¦318664 of the \add ≈world\add*.
\q1 Among them are the blind¦318668 and the lame,
\q1 and pregnant¦318670 \add #women\add* together with those giving birth¦318671.
